<p>Reports Micronaut Cache annotations where the value of the <code>parameters</code> attribute contains names of undefined method
  parameters.</p>
<p>The following annotations are supported:</p>
<ul>
  <li><code>io.micronaut.cache.annotation.Cacheable</code></li>
  <li><code>io.micronaut.cache.annotation.CachePut</code></li>
  <li><code>io.micronaut.cache.annotation.CacheInvalidate</code></li>
</ul>
<p><b>Example:</b></p>
<pre><code lang="java">
  @CachePut(parameters = "myParameter") // Error: Cannot resolve symbol 'myParameter'
  public String cachedMethod(String name_is_not_equal_to_myParameter) {
    return "...";
  }
</code></pre>
</body>
